data.description: Come view this lovely bi-level home that offers 4 generously sized bedrooms and two full baths magnificently located in the Streamwood  Green neighborhood near plenty of shopping and close to highways. This home has a welcoming open space floor plan, Fenced Yard, 2 1/2 attached car garage near schools and parks.  All appliances stay and easy to show with a courtesy 2 hour window you can secure a viewing for your client with ease.
